<div class="tip_number">TIP 2</div>
<div class="tip_contents">
            Brain tumors usually cause headaches that get progressively worse. These headaches will sometimes worsen in the middle of the night. Other signs, such as seizures, weakness, or loss of sensation in a part of the body, can also occur.
        </div>

